{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-211-Bonjour-Network-Discovery-and-Connectivity"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Bonjour, also known as zero-configuration networking, enables automatic discovery of computers, devices, and services on IP networks. A wide range of Apple’s products-from iMacs and MacBooks to AirPort Base Stations and Time Capsules, Apple TVs to iPhones, iPod touches and iPads-use Bonjour for streamlined and reliable networking. Learn how to use Bonjour to make it easy for your applications to publish, discover, and resolve network services.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC11","title":"Bonjour Network Discovery and Connectivity","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/211\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"kind":"article","sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-211-bonjour-network-discovery-and-connectivity"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/211/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011